{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十六回\"久别重逢\"。竹叶青与老和尚密谋让燕十三与谢晓峰在无意中相见。谢晓峰在院中为小弟取出肩胛中的枯竹剑剑尖，小弟透露天尊就是其母慕容秋荻，曾安排单亦飞、柳枯竹、富贵神仙手、仇二等人围杀谢晓峰。小弟不愿认父，用被蒙住谢晓峰头部后逃走。慕容秋荻深夜现身，先是以冷酷姿态宣布要亲手杀谢晓峰，却在攻击中展露真情，被谢晓峰夺剑制服后倒入其怀中。二人回忆十五年前初遇、第二次分别的往事，感情纠葛难解。慕容秋荻以退为进，先假装要谢晓峰带她走，随后揭露真意：天尊是她苦心经营的基业，绝不会为谢晓峰解散，孩子也不会带来给他。她以嘲讽收尾，冷酷地拒绝了谢晓峰的幻想。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，燕十三，当然是燕十三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "普天之下，除了夫人外，只有他知道谢晓峰剑法中的破绽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是他自从在绿水湖中刻舟沉剑后，江湖中就再也没有人见到过他的行踪，他怎么会替夫人去找谢晓峰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "他不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "谢晓峰会去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "也不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "可是我保证他们一定会在无意中相见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老和尚",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "真的无意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_lao_he_shang",
      "text": "是有情？还是无情？是有意？还是无意？这些事有谁能分得清？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你走吧！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们走的本就不是一条路，你走你的，我走我的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你不能换一条路走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这一剑本该是刺在你身上的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你虽然替我治了伤，我也用不着感谢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你用不着……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以我要走的时候，你也不该留我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你几时要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "以前你就见过我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "虽然人没见过，却见过别人替你画的一幅像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你有没有告诉过别人，你已认出了我？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只告诉过一个人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "天尊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "所以她就订下这计划来杀我？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她知道要杀你并不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "单亦飞、柳枯竹、富贵神仙手，和那老和尚都是天尊的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "仇二也是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "天尊就是你母亲？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错，天尊就是我母亲，现在我也用不着瞒你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你本来就不必瞒我，我们之间，本就不该有秘密。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "为什么？你真的不知道为什么？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "那么我问你，既然你母亲要杀我，你为什么要救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "已经有很多年了，是十五年？还是十六年？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "看样子你还是没有变，还是不喜欢说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我们还有什么话好说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有了……没有了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们之间若是真的已无话可说，我为什么要来找你？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我来，只因为我要带走那个孩子，你以前既然不要他，现在又何必来惹他，让他痛苦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我来，也因为我要告诉你，我一定要你死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "而且这一次我要让你死在我自己手里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "天尊杀人，又何必自己出手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "杀别人我从不自己出手，你却是例外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还记不记得，我们第一次相见的时候，我也要杀你，你也夺过了我的剑，就像这样抱着我！",
      "tone": "哀怨",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就是谢家的三少爷？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你怎么知道我是？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为除了谢家的三少外，没有人能在一招间夺下我的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不管你心里怎么样想，我总忘不了那一天，因为就在那一天，我就把我整个人都给了你，迷迷糊糊的给了你，你却一去就没了消息。",
      "tone": "哀怨",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "等到我们第二次见面的时候，我已订了亲，你是来送贺礼的。",
      "tone": "哀怨",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那时我虽然恨你，怨你，可是一见到你，我就没了主意。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以就在我订亲的第二天晚上，我又迷迷糊糊的跟着你走了，想不到你又甩下了我，又一去就没消息。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我心里虽然更恨你，可是……可是……我还是希望你能像以前一样，再骗我一次，再把我带走，就算这次你杀了我，我也不怨你。",
      "tone": "哀怨",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你以为我已变了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是不管我在别人面前变成了个什么样的人，对你，我是永远不会变的。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你是不是一定要我杀了你？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要你高兴，你就杀了我吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你的伤口还在流血，至少也该让我先替你包好。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "虽然这是我叫人去伤了你的，可是那完全是另外一回事，只要你开口，我随时都可以去替你杀了那些人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你心里在想什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想要我解散天尊，带回那个孩子，安安静静的过几年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道我心里在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我在想，你真是个呆子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "呆子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知不知道天尊是我花了多少苦心才建立的？我怎么能随随便便就将它毁了？你既然已不要那孩子，我为什么要带来给你？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你至少也该想想，我现在是什么地位？什么身分？难道还会去替你煮饭洗衣裳？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 375,
